9. read out NTTtable
--------------------

- get pv list in a host
  pvlist <host>

ex)
khkim@lcls-dev3 ~ $ pvlist cpu-b084-sp18
TST:SYS2:4:NTTBL1
TST:SYS2:4:NTTBL2
TST:SYS2:4:NTTBL3
TST:SYS2:4:NTTBL4


- check up pv structure
  pvinfo <pv name, NTTable PV name>
ex)
khkim@lcls-dev3 ~ $ pvinfo TST:SYS2:4:NTTBL1
